 女孩們的心事還真奇怪<br />\n<br />\n愛真奇怪 來來來來來來來來來 噢嘿噢<br />\n來來來來來來來來來來來 噢<br />\n唉 算了 回家吧"},{"pid":"e604c2d0ced87072d047ef60345ae37c98c3d7d3","tid":1846012,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f33c968bfb2e8d343cbe73c089cab1e044a3f1","tid":1846012,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5gg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=451c65f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"df1be4ec3656a98c6d144124dc213000d18ef92a","tid":1846012,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}